description: Sage Gold Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, development, and production of mineral properties in Canada. It explores for gold, copper, silver, zinc, and lead deposits. Its primary properties include the Clavos gold project located in the Timmins mining district in Northeastern Ontario; and the Onaman property comprising the Lynx project and the Headway project located in the Beardmore-Geraldton Gold Camp. Sage Gold Inc. was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
